  "description": {
    "zh": "又接到一个订单，这次是个退役特种兵，他想要一把 AK-105。\n\n要求挺多：手感好、后坐小、不太重、能装下至少 45 发子弹，还要有 800 米以上的射程。另外还必须装上两样东西：两脚架和战术配件。\n\nAK-105 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 325\n - 重量小于 4.5 公斤\n - 人机功效 60 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 85 %\n - 弹匣容量 45 或更多\n - “射击场”距离 800米 或更多\n - 任意 脚架\n - 任意 战术设备",
    "en": "I got another customer - Former special forces - Asking for an AK-105 assault rifle. Fairly ergonomic, not too much recoil, not too heavy, obviously...\nCapable of holding at least fourty-five rounds and be able to take shots from eight-hundred meters away or more. It needs to have a bipod and a tactical device aswell.\n\nAK-105 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 325\n - Weight less than 4.5 KG\n - Ergonomics 60 or higher\n - Durability higher than 85 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 45 or more\n - Sighting Range of 800 Meters or more\n - A Bipod\n - A Tactical Device"
  },
